metadata.description: Ibotta, Inc. operates as a technology company that offers Ibotta Performance Network (IPN) that allows consumer packaged goods brands to deliver digital promotions to consumers. It offers promotional services to publishers, retailers, and advertisers through the IPN. The company was formerly known as Zing Enterprises, Inc. and changed its name to Ibotta, Inc. in 2012. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Denver, Colorado.
